(1, '3', '欢迎使用幽幽草堂博客系统！', 1, 1, 1, 5, 441, 1311463853, 1343819917, ' 系统,草堂,模块,博客', 3, '<p>欢迎使用幽幽草堂博客系统！</p><p>月下草堂博客系统是幽幽草堂主人--冷月十三基于PHP框架Yii Framework的开山之作，该系统遵循一切模块化的思想进行相关开发，所有模块相对独立，多个模块组合即是一个可用的应用系统。<br /></p><p></p><br /><div style="position: absolute; display: none; z-index: 9999;" id="livemargins_control"><img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-horizontal.png" style="position: absolute;left:-77px;top:-5px" alt="" height="5" width="77" />	<img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-vertical.png" style="position: absolute;left:0;top:-5px;" alt="" />	<img id="monitor-play-button" src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-play-button.png" style="position: absolute;left:1px;top:0;opacity:0.5;cursor:pointer" alt="" /></div><div style="position: absolute; display: none; z-index: 9999;" id="livemargins_control"><img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-horizontal.png" style="position: absolute;left:-77px;top:-5px" alt="" height="5" width="77" />	<img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-vertical.png" style="position: absolute;left:0;top:-5px;" alt="" />	<img id="monitor-play-button" src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-play-button.png" style="position: absolute;left:1px;top:0;opacity:0.5;cursor:pointer" alt="" /></div><div style="position: absolute; display: none; z-index: 9999;" id="livemargins_control"><img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-horizontal.png" style="position: absolute;left:-77px;top:-5px" alt="" height="5" width="77" />	<img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-vertical.png" style="position: absolute;left:0;top:-5px;" alt="" />	<img id="monitor-play-button" src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-play-button.png" style="position: absolute;left:1px;top:0;opacity:0.5;cursor:pointer" alt="" /></div><div style="position: absolute; display: none; z-index: 9999;" id="livemargins_control"><img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-horizontal.png" style="position: absolute;left:-77px;top:-5px" alt="" height="5" width="77" />	<img src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-background-vertical.png" style="position: absolute;left:0;top:-5px;" alt="" />	<img id="monitor-play-button" src="/chrome:/livemargins/skin/monitor-play-button.png" style="position: absolute;left:1px;top:0;opacity:0.5;cursor:pointer" alt="" /></div>'),
(3, '21', 'YII中的RBAC权限,用数据库存item', 1, 1, 1, 5, 363, 1317563702, 1343818032, 'Yii,配置,数据库,RBAC权限', 3, '<br />在system/web/auth下找到相应的sql导放到数据库中<br /><p>配置</p><div style="border:solid #ccc 1px;width:98%;overflow:auto;"><div style="background-color:#ddd; border-bottom:solid 1px #ccc; line-height:1.5em; text-indent:0.5em;">php代码</div><pre class="brush:php;">''authManager'' =&gt; array(\r\n''class'' =&gt; ''CDbAuthManager'',\r\n''connectionID'' =&gt; ''db'',\r\n),</pre></div><br />如果在sql中导入的三个表的表名不是默认的，需要在这上边的配置中配置，具体的看api<br /><br /><div style="border:solid #ccc 1px;width:98%;overflow:auto;"><div style="background-color:#ddd; border-bottom:solid 1px #ccc; line-height:1.5em; text-indent:0.5em;">php代码</div><pre class="brush:php;">$auth=Yii::app()-&gt;authManager;\r\n//$auth-&gt;createOperation("post",''postpost'');\r\n//$auth-&gt;createTask("post","posts");\r\n$auth-&gt;createRole("post","post");\r\nauth-&gt;assign("post",''demo'');\r\nif(Yii::app()-&gt;user-&gt;checkAccess("post")){\r\necho "yes";\r\nelse{\r\necho "no";\r\n}</pre></div><br />这种情况下三者是一样的<br /><br />'),
