round-color:transparent; text-indent:28px">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; color:rgb(51,51,51); background-color:transparent; text-indent:28px">\r\n<a target="_blank" href="http://www.pvmgarage.com/2010/04/touch-the-future-create-an-elegant-website-with-hmtl-5-and-css3/" style="color:rgb(0,66,118); text-decoration:underline">Create a elegant website with HTML5 and CSS3</a></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; color:rgb(51,51,51); background-color:transparent; text-indent:28px">\r\n</p>\r\n<center><img class="fit-image" alt="分享最好的HTML5编码教程和参考手册" src="http://images.51cto.com/files/uploadimg/20111027/14341513.jpg" style="border-top-width:medium; border-right-width:medium; border-bottom-width:medium; border-left-width:medium; border-style:initial; border-color:initial; border-top-style:none; border-right-style:none; border-bottom-style:none; border-left-style:none; border-color:initial; width:396px; height:218px" width="305" height="30" /></center>\r\n<center><br />\r\n</center>\r\n<center><br />\r\n</center>\r\n<center><br />\r\n</center>\r\n<center><br />\r\n</center>\r\n<center>文章来源：&nbsp;<a href="http://www.gbin1.com/technology/html/20101019bestreferencesandtutorialstostartcodingwithhtml5/index.html">http://www.gbin1.com/technology/html/20101019bestreferencesandtutorialstostartcodingwithhtml5/index.html</a></center><br />'),
(53, '189', 'Ubuntu 11.10 安装后要做的12件事情', 1, 1, 1, 5, 229, 1321851109, 1343735797, ' 标键,大小,文章,快捷键,命令', 3, '<a title="" href="http://www.uplooking.com/page/ocp-rhce20111001.php" target="_blank"><br /></a><div id="content"><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> 11.10 在10月13日发布。Ubuntu有很多变化，我们不再赘述。除去《<a title="" href="http://www.linuxidc.com/Linux/2011-10/44598.htm" target="_self">Ubuntu 11.10 专题总结</a>》外，本文又总结了《Ubuntu 11.10 安装后要做的12件事情》。希望对各位有所指导帮助。 \r\n<p>（“<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> ＊＊安装后要做的＊＊件事情”几乎成了Ubuntu每次发布的惯例。原因在Ubuntu的流行，吸引人们不断折腾）</p><table width="97%" align="center" border="0"><tbody><tr><td colspan="3"><br /></td></tr></tbody></table><br /><span id="more-3932"></span><br /><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162661565.png" rel="slb[slb_3932]"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3933" title="thingstodo_after_installing_ubuntu_oneric" alt="" src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162661566.png" width="300" height="175" /></a>\r\n<h3>#1，安装Restricted Extras</h3>\r\n<p>从<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> 11.04 版本开始，我们就可以在Ubuntu安装过程中安装一些编码包，如Adobe Flash\\<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/audio/index.htm" title="MP3">MP3</a>等等。（但是必须连接网络，如果网速很慢，这回延长安装时间，建议直接下一步）<br /><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162661563.png" rel="slb[slb_3932]"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3934" title="Screenshot" alt="" src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162661564.png" width="300" height="225" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>#2，升级软件源</h3>\r\n<p>安装<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> 11.10后，第一件事情就是更新软件列表。打开终端（快捷键：Ctrl+Alt+T）：</p><pre>sudo apt-get update &amp;&amp; sudo apt-get upgrade</pre>\r\n<h3>#3，安装<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> Restricted Extras</h3>\r\n<p>安装<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> Restricted Extras软件包后，我们就可以播放<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/audio/index.htm" title="MP3">MP3</a>,avi,Flash等了。</p>\r\n<p>直接输入命令：</p><pre>sudo apt-get install <a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a>-restricted-extras</pre>\r\n<h3>#4，支持DVD播放</h3>\r\n<p>第#3步可以解决大部分问题，但是要支持DVD播放，还需要安装：libdvdcss2:</p><pre>sudo wget --output-document=/etc/apt/sources.list.d/medibuntu.list http://www.medibuntu.org/sources.list.d/$(lsb_release -cs).list &amp;&amp; sudo apt-get --quiet update &amp;&amp; sudo apt-get --yes --quiet --allow-unauthenticated install medibuntu-keyring &amp;&amp; sudo apt-get --quiet update\r\nsudo apt-get install libdvdcss2</pre>\r\n<h3>#5，升级显卡驱动</h3>\r\n<p>在Unity搜索“附件驱动”，打开，激活推荐驱动即可。<br /><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162661561.png" rel="slb[slb_3932]"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3935" title="drivers_ubuntu1110" alt="" src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162661562.png" width="300" height="280" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>#6，安装CCSM</h3>\r\n<p>安装CCSM，可以启动<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> 桌面特效和3D加速效果。</p>\r\n<p>命令：</p><pre>sudo apt-get install compizconfig-settings-manager</pre></div><div id="content"><h3>#7，Unity 快捷键操作</h3>\r\n<p>徽标键：打开Dash面板；<br />长按徽标键，唤醒启动器；<br />Alt+F1,从Unity启动器启动程序；<br />Alt+F2,打开Dash面板，输入命令；<br />Super+F:打开文件／文件夹；</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650901.png" alt="" border="0" /><br /></p><table width="97%" align="center" border="0"><tbody><tr><td colspan="3"><br /></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<h3>#8，设置Unity 顶部面板透明：</h3>\r\n<p>启动CCSM（徽标键+a，搜索ccsm），点击启动，选择“<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> Unity 插件”，依次打开“Experimental tab—Panel Opacity”，即可设定透明度。<br /><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650902.png" rel="slb[slb_3932]"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3936" title="Screenshot-2" alt="" src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650903.png" width="300" height="190" /></a></p>\r\n<p>同时，我们可以设置“Launcher Icon size”,即启动器上图标大小。</p>\r\n<h3>#9，设定桌面大小</h3>\r\n<p>徽标键+S，显示工作窗口。还是启动CCSM，在”常规选项”,”桌面尺寸”标签下，即可设定值。<br /><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650908.png" rel="slb[slb_3932]"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3939" title="unity_workspaces" alt="" src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650909.png" width="300" height="175" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>#10，在Unity启动器上添加快捷方式（Quicklist）</h3>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650906.png" rel="slb[slb_3932]"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3937" title="Unity_quicklists" alt="" src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650907.png" width="271" height="300" /></a></p>\r\n<p>快捷方式（Quicklist）是<a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/topicnews.aspx?tid=2" title="Ubuntu">Ubuntu</a> 11.10 一个默认功能。具体设定参考文章<a title="" href="http://www.linuxidc.com/Linux/2011-05/35664.htm" target="_blank">Ubuntu 11.04 Unity所需的6个快捷列表<br /></a></p>\r\n<h3>#11，启用Unity Grab 功能</h3>\r\n<p>Unity Grab可用于调整窗口大小，尤其对触摸屏设备特别有帮助。</p>\r\n<p>还是启动CCSM，找到Png，选中，然后在“未分类”中选中“Unity MT Grab Handles”，点击选项，开启，选择快捷键设定即可。</p>\r\n<p>效果如下：<br /><a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650904.png" rel="slb[slb_3932]"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3938" title="unity_grab_handles" alt="" src="http://www.linuxidc.com/upload/2011_10/111013162650905.png" width="300" height="212" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>#12，安装插件扩展</h3>\r\n<p>如ClassicMenu Indicator等等，具体参考下面文章。<br />推荐文章：<a title="" href="http://www.linuxidc.com/Linux/2011-06/37829.htm" target="_blank">Ubuntu 11.04流行的10款应用插件</a></p></div><br />');
