(87, '199,200', 'CSS自定义字体', 1, 1, 1, 5, 257, 1324186110, 1343817575, ' 字体,序列,如下,对象,嵌入', 3, '<p><div class="cont">\r\n			<strong>设置或检索用于对象中文本的字体名称序列。</strong>\r\n			<ul><li>序列可包含嵌入字体。请参阅<a href="http://www.css88.com/book/css/css/rules/@font-face.htm">@font-face</a>规则。</li><li>对应的脚本特性为<strong>fontFamily</strong>。</li></ul>\r\n		</div></p><p>使用如下：<br /></p><p>@font-face{</p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;font-family:YH;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;src:url(http://domain/fonts/MSYH.TTF);<br />}<br />body{font-family:''YH'';}<br />'),
