INSERT INTO `uu_solution` (`sol_id`, `sol_pid`, `sol_content`, `sol_hits`, `sol_created`, `sol_uid`) VALUES
(1, 2, '<p>解决方案来自：<a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/bynet/archive/2009/11/13/1602491.html">http://www.cnblogs.com/bynet/archive/2009/11/13/1602491.html</a>&nbsp;</p><p>把如上代码修改为：</p><pre class="brush:js;toolbar:false;">$(".category input[type=checkbox]").change(function(){\n//      alert($("#Article_arc_cids").val());\n        var str = "";\n        $(".category input[type=checkbox]:checked").each(function(){          \n            console.log($(this).attr("checked")); \n                  \n            str +=","+$(this).val();\n                \n        });\n              \n        str = str.substring(1,str.length);          \n      \n        $("#Article_arc_cids").val(str);\n      \n    });</pre><p><br /></p>', 0, 1340107572, 5),
(2, 3, '<p>终于发现了，原来是因为冲突了，我把自己做的插件和ueditor放在一起了，于是便不能正常显示了。既然冲突了，保留其一就可以解决问题了。</p>', 0, 1340456617, 5),
(3, 8, '<p>这里先记录一种再简单不过的方法：</p><p>先读出所有的日志创建时间，然后遍历处理成如下格式的数组：$result[$year][$month]，如此就完成了。</p><pre class="brush:as3;toolbar:false;">$temp = $result = array();\n \n$criteria = new CDbCriteria(array(\n    ''select''=&gt;''pubdate'',\n    ''order''=&gt;''pubdate DESC''\n));\n \n$model = Blog::model()-&gt;findAll($criteria);\n \nforeach ($model as $data)\n{\n    $temp[] = $data-&gt;pubdate;\n}\n \nif (is_array($temp))\n{\n    foreach ($temp as $time)\n    {\n        $y = gmdate(''Y'', $time);\n        $m = gmdate(''n'', $time);\n         \n        $result[$year][$month] += 1;\n    }\n}</pre><p>此方法来自于：<a href="http://www.zendstudio.net/archives/how-archives-the-blogs/?replytocom=195">http://www.zendstudio.net/archives/how-archives-the-blogs/?replytocom=195</a>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 1343801596, 5),
(4, 9, '<pre class="brush:php;toolbar:false;">ignore_user_abort();//关掉浏览器，PHP脚本也可以继续执行.\nset_time_limit(0);// 通过set_time_limit(0)可以让程序无限制的执行下去\n$interval=60*30;// 每隔半小时运行\ndo{\n    //这里是你要执行的代码    \n    sleep($interval);// 等待5分钟\n}while(true);</pre><p>解决方案来自：<a href="http://www.oschina.net/code/snippet_105076_3962">http://www.oschina.net/code/snippet_105076_3962</a>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 1343829179, 5);
